ain/WakeupCallBoss" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/WakeupCallBoss">is also one of the first optional bosses</a>.</li><li> nao's concert uses <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/HyperdimensionNeptuniaMk2" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/HyperdimensionNeptuniaMk2">Hyperdimension Neptunia mk2</a></em> opening. <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/SceneryPorn" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/SceneryPorn">It is glorious.</a></li><li> The last episode starts with a reenactment of the Conquest End from <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/HyperdimensionNeptuniaMk2" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/VideoGame/HyperdimensionNeptuniaMk2">Hyperdimension Neptunia mk2</a></em> <span class="spoiler" title="you can set spoilers visible by default on your profile"> It's <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/AllJustADream" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/AllJustADream">All Just a Dream</a>.</span></li></ul></li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/NiceGirl" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/NiceGirl">Nice Girls</a> Nepgear, Uni, Rom and Compa are all made to this since they're shown to be friendly.</li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/NoIndoorVoice" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/NoIndoorVoice">No Indoor Voice</a>:<div class="indent"><strong><span class="spoiler" title="you can set spoilers visible by default on your profile">Peashy</span> (raising)</strong>: <em>AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA</em> (pause, <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/UpToEleven" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/UpToEleven">then raising higher</a>) <em>AAAAAAAAA</em></div><div class="indent"><strong>Neptune</strong> (<a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/NoFourthWall" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/NoFourthWall">at viewer</a>): Who is that?!</div></li><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/NoSell" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/NoSell">No-Sell</a>:<ul><li> Everyone that fi